            <history-note id="DLM292561"><amended-provision>Section 296(5)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>28 September 1993</amendment-date>, by section 13 of the <amending-leg>Te Ture Whenua Maori Amendment Act (No 2) 1993/Maori Land Amendment Act (No 2) 1993</amending-leg> (1993 No 104).</history-note>
